name: Avriel Harry
description: I am emotionally stable, kindhearted and accurate with a good sense of humor. I have a positive attitude of life. I value life and try to spend every minute of it happily. I can easily adapt to new situations and people, I am flexible in relationship and understanding. I always try to be in "the shoes of other people" not to judge but to understanding the actions to find them. I am gentle and that is me.
